James Carothers `` Jim '' Garrison -LRB- born Earling Carothers Garrison ; November 20 , 1921 -- October 21 , 1992 -RRB- was the District Attorney of Orleans Parish , Louisiana , from 1962 to 1973 .
A member of the Democratic Party , he is best known for his investigations into the assassination of President John F. Kennedy .
He was played by Kevin Costner in Oliver Stone 's JFK .